@startuml
title Devils Resting - Состояния сообщения
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam nodesep 45
skinparam ranksep 55
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam ArrowColor #687385
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.1
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam state {
  BorderColor #9fb0c7
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  FontColor #1f2937
}
skinparam note {
  BorderColor #d7dee8
  BackgroundColor #fbfcfe
  FontColor #445066
}

state "Нет черновика" as NoDraft
state "Редактирование черновика" as Drafting
state "Файлы в очереди" as FilesQueued
state "Загрузка файлов" as Uploading
state "Готово к отправке" as ReadyToSend
state "Отправка" as Sending
state "Отправка отклонена" as Rejected
state "Опубликовано" as Published
state "Отредактировано" as Edited
state "Есть read tracking" as ReadTracked
state "Удалено" as Deleted

[*] --> NoDraft

NoDraft --> Drafting : фокус на composer
Drafting --> FilesQueued : добавлены файлы
FilesQueued --> Uploading : uploadAttachments
Uploading --> FilesQueued : отмена или частичный сбой
Uploading --> ReadyToSend : получены upload id

Drafting --> Sending : отправка текста
ReadyToSend --> Sending : текст и upload id

Sending : ws chat_message\nили finalize attachments
Sending --> Published : сообщение сохранено\nвложения привязаны
Sending --> Rejected : validation / permission /\nrate limit / slow mode
Rejected --> Drafting : исправить и повторить

Published --> Edited : edit_message
Edited --> Published : изменения разосланы

Published --> ReadTracked : mark_read / read_receipt
Edited --> ReadTracked : поздние read receipts

Published --> Deleted : delete_message
Edited --> Deleted : delete_message
ReadTracked --> Edited : позднее редактирование
ReadTracked --> Deleted : позднее удаление

Deleted --> [*]

note right of Published
После публикации сообщение
может получать реакции,
pins и inbox notifications
без смены базового состояния.
end note
@enduml
